(107, 12, 'Il malocchio', 'Il malocchio', 1888, 'The protagonist of the story is Vincenzo Albagi, who since the age of twelve has dreamed of becoming emperor like Napoleon. He lives in a small provincial town with his parents. His father Geraldo is a wine merchant, a man satisfied with his bourgeois condition, who has been able to enrich himself and his family by doing business.', 20.00, '9788874302512', 'book_cover\\italo_svevo\\il_malocchio.jpg'),
