(125, 23, 'Chagrin école', 'Diario di scuola', 2007, 'Everything you need to know about Chagrin école by Daniel Pennac! Find the essence of the work in a complete and detailed reading sheet, with a summary, a study of the characters, keys to reading and lines of thought. Written in a clear and accessible way, the reading sheet first offers a summary of the book, then studies the  characters  whose portrait is painted by Pennac: that of the dunce, the teacher, and more generally teachers and their students.', 15.00, '9782200500955', 'book_cover\\daniel_pennac\\chagrin_ecole.jpg'),
(126, 23, 'La loi di rêveur', 'La legge del sognatore', 2020, 'Daniel Pennac is a clever, a manipulator, who under the pretext of telling you his dreams leads you and loses you in a chaotic story where a cow would not recognize her calf!', 20.00, '9782200500917', 'book_cover\\daniel_pennac\\la_loi_du.jpg'),
(127, 24, 'Cromwell', 'Cromwell', 1827, 'In 1642, the army of Charles I Stuart faces that of the faithful to the parliament which refused the king to grant the necessary funds for the war against Scotland. At the head of the parliamentary army is Oliver Cromwell.', 20.00, '9782200501723', 'book_cover\\victor_hugo\\cromwell.jpg'),
