(156, 34, 'Fairy Tail', 'Fairy Tail', 2006, 'The world of Earth-land is home to numerous guilds where wizards[b] apply their magic for paid job requests. Natsu Dragneel, a Dragon Slayer wizard from the Fairy Tail guild, explores the Kingdom of Fiore in search of his missing adoptive father, the dragon Igneel. During his journey, he befriends a young celestial wizard named Lucy Heartfilia and invites her to join Fairy Tail. ', 5.00, '9784192039185', 'book_cover\\hiro_mashima\\fairy_tail.jpg'),
