(171, 37, 'Robots And Witches', 'Robot e Streghe', 2009, 'Bitter about life cruel games, the main character cant understand their conflicting feelings when a new face at work/college captures their interest.Soon becoming smitten with the love interest, the main character begins to feel conflicted when another charming stranger entices them out and causes the love interest to suspect the main character is cheating on them.', 20.00, '9785700084284', 'book_cover\\nazar_mordvinov\\robot_and_witches.jpg'),
(172, 38, 'Murder With A Goal', 'Lo scopo di uccidere', 1900, 'At the top of their game, the main character forms a new relationship when they are presented with a position of power that results in them working for a large, international organisation.Refusing to back down, the main character, public enemy number one, comes up with a cunning plan to find out the truth.In the end, after being permanently disabled, the main character is forced to go on the run after committing numerous crimes, and vows to get justice.', 20.00, '9785700083874', 'book_cover\\catherine_artemyveva\\murder.jpg'),
(173, 38, 'Fortune With Silver', 'Fortuna argentea', 1903, 'Your main character is a man in his late thirties, who can be quite stubborn. The story begins in a penthouse apartment. An abandoned dog is given a home. It a story about secrecy. Your character gets into a competition with another character.', 15.00, '9785700083294', 'book_cover\\catherine_artemyveva\\silver.jpg'),
(174, 38, 'Hurting The Darkness', 'Scontro con il buio', 1910, 'Having enjoyed a peaceful life up until now, the main character is tasked with obtaining an important item when their village is being subjected to a devastating attack by an enemy nation; it requires them to re-evaluate their current lifestyle.', 15.00, '9785700084666', 'book_cover\\catherine_artemyveva\\darkness.jpg'),
