(176, 39, 'Agent Of The Plague', 'Agenti della Piaga', 1933, 'Living peacefully with no knowledge of the growing threat beyond their homelands, the main character realises there is more to their life when they are accused of being the leader of an enemy movement which launches an attack; it is destined to be opposed by one born under their circumstances.Driven by rage, the main character, with an experienced mentor, struggles to figure out what is right or wrong.In the end, after a close encounter with the enemy, the main character sacrifices themselves to save someone else.', 15.00, '9785700083157', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\pleague.jpg'),
(177, 39, 'Horses Of The East', 'RUM - Cavallo bianco', 1939, 'A determined hard worker with no time for love, the main character life is turned upside down when a long lost friend returns, asking them for help.', 15.00, '9785700084147', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\horse.jpg'),
(178, 39, 'Armies Of The Light', 'Gemme di Luce', 1941, 'Bitter about being unable to find love, the main character emotions rise when a long lost friend returns, asking them for help.Doing their best to repress their growing feelings, the main character forms a bitter rivalry when another person with much better chances than the main character shows up and begins competing for the love interest attention.', 15.00, '9785700084178', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\light.jpg'),
(179, 39, 'Owls And Wolves', 'Gufi e Lupi', 1943, 'Stuck enduring the daily grind, the main character is soon hunted by forces far stronger than them when they learn of the dragon that steadily grows in power and threatens their land; it requires them to give up their current lifestyle.After pretending that nothing is wrong, the main character, after trying to drown out their sorrows, comes up with a cunning plan to find out the truth.', 15.00, '9785700083287', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\owls_and_wolf.jpg'),
(180, 39, 'Spiders And Priests', 'Ragni e Preti', 1944, 'Having never been in love before, the main character suddenly loses all focus when they misreads the signs given off by another character.', 25.00, '9785700084406', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\spider_and_priest.jpg'),
(181, 39, 'Origin Without Faith', 'Nessun legame', 1943, 'A computer programmer makes it big by playing basketball.', 25.00, '9785700084062', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\faith.jpg'),
(182, 39, 'Hope Of The Stars', 'Speranza brillante', 1944, 'Your main character is a man in his late thirties, who can be quite cruel. The story begins in a boxing club. Someone is being blackmailed. It a story about loneliness. Your character is tested to the limits of physical endurance.', 13.00, '9785700083171', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\hope.jpg'),
(183, 39, 'Sailing Into The Graveyard', 'Visita al cimitero', 1944, 'An all-American girl meets someone she thought had died at a boarding school for girls.', 13.00, '9785700084802', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\graveyard.jpg'),
(184, 39, 'Force Of The Light', 'Forze della luce', 1946, 'A simple peasant with little knowledge of the world, the main character life suddenly changes when they return home to find that their homeland is being burnt to the ground by an enemy attack; it requires them to travel around the world.Driven by rage, the main character, after surviving a series of failed of assassination attempts, struggles to stay ahead of a deadly pursuer hot on their trail.', 6.00, '9785700084192', 'book_cover\\stella_golubova\\force_light.jpg'),
(185, 40, 'Shield Of The Eclipse', 'Scudo lunare', 2000, 'The president is born again in an asylum.', 10.00, '9785700085076', 'book_cover\\iskander_efimov\\shield.jpg'),
(186, 40, 'Blinded In My Friends', 'Amizicia Cieca', 2003, 'Having always known about the rocky past between their race and another, the main character loses what dearest to them when a mysterious character forces them into a situation well outside their control; it will eventually ruin their life.Brave enough to go forward, the main character, without thinking ahead, struggles to separate the truth from the lies.', 15.00, '9785700084239', 'book_cover\\iskander_efimov\\blinded.jpg'),
(187, 40, 'Flee To The Elements', 'Con gli elementi', 2009, 'Your main character is a young woman in her late teens, who is very eccentric. The story begins in a doctors surgery. A baby is born in mysterious circumstances. It a story about stubbornness. Your character attempts to keep a low profile.', 20.00, '9785700084468', 'book_cover\\iskander_efimov\\flee.jpg'),
(188, 40, 'The Bane of the Wicked', 'Le ossa della stregha', 2012, 'Having recently been plagued by visions, the main character must fight to protect what they love when they learn of the dark lord that steadily grows in power that seeks to exact their revenge on those who imprisoned them.', 15.00, '9785700083836', 'book_cover\\iskander_efimov\\the_bane.jpg'),
